snippet.title: The Division Resurgence: New Factions, New Stories, and Gameplay
snippet.description: Tom Clancy's The Division Resurgence is coming to Android and iOS devices soon. We had a chat with Executive Producer Fabrice Navrez about new enemies, factions, and the importance of this installment to the Division universe.
